/* STDLIB/iii/aether/xenos.iii -- XENOS: the membrane of xenia.
 *
 * The law of xenia is safe hospitality to the stranger: the guest is received
 * with honor, but under the house's law; the house speaks one tongue; the door
 * remembers every knock.  XENOS is III's one door to the foreign world.  The
 * foreign (RFC 8259 JSON, the world's lingua franca) enters ONLY transduced
 * into EIDOLOS -- the house's universal reasoning language -- and is JUDGED by
 * III's own re-derivation, never by trust in the input's shape.  What cannot
 * be made coherent is REFUSED and remembered; what is not even speech is
 * UNHEARD and counted; and the SAME DOOR EMITS: the house's knowledge leaves
 * through the identical boundary form it admits, so two houses' doors can
 * speak to each other and verify every word.
 *
 * THREE GRADES OF GUEST, ONE DOOR (xn_admit):
 *   CONFORMING  an envelope object {"speak":"eidolos","axiom":A,"address":D,
 *               "claims":[...]} whose axiom equals the house's Logos-Axiom
 *               address (THE HANDSHAKE -- "compare axioms before merging
 *               scrolls", now enforced at the door) and whose stated address
 *               re-derives from its claims.  A lying address or geometry is
 *               REFUSED (corruption cannot hide at the door -- the logos-wire
 *               law lifted to the foreign wire); a foreign axiom is REFUSED
 *               (the guest lives under a different soul; quarantined for
 *               future diplomacy, never merged).
 *   UNSIGNED    a bare claim-array ["[a < b]", ...]: the guest speaks the
 *               language without credentials; admitted on coherence alone.
 *   STRANGER    ANY other JSON value: the TOTAL STRUCTURAL TRANSDUCTION
 *               renders the tree as claims -- containment is `<`, and a leaf
 *               value rides INSIDE its thing's phrase as a measure or word
 *               (the standing-speaker idiom [kardia 124:1766 = derived]), so
 *               no false identities can be minted: {"a":1,"b":1} never
 *               unravels a = b.  Structural scrolls are coherent BY
 *               CONSTRUCTION (a tree of strict containment); the judgment
 *               still runs, never assumed.
 *
 * THE STRANGER'S NAME IS ITS CONTENT: a structural guest is rooted under the
 * thing `stranger H L` where H L is the split idfold of its CANONICAL
 * RE-EMISSION through verba/json (whitespace and escape clothing removed; the
 * door hears the value, not the formatting).  Member order remains part of
 * the utterance (eidolos itself orients by content precisely because order is
 * speech, not knowledge: the claims are order-free, the name hears the
 * utterance).  The rendering is a QUOTIENT (case-folded words, fold-spoken
 * alien tokens) and the quotient is WITNESSED by that root name -- coarse
 * claims, fine name: the coarseness law of arm 84, honored at the door.
 *
 * THE JUDGMENT IS RE-DERIVATION: transduce -> read -> lawcheck -> address;
 * then the canonical text is RE-READ from scratch and must re-derive the SAME
 * address (the fixpoint judged live at every admission, never assumed).  All
 * refusals are NAMED and COUNTED (broken / cycle / lying / soul / throat);
 * an over-envelope stranger is refused WHOLE, never truncated.
 *
 * THE GUEST-BOOK (STDLIB/data/xenos.gbk): every knock is remembered as a
 * self-verifying EIDOLOS event line `<addr> <event>\n` whose address must
 * re-derive from its text (tamper = the whole book refuses).  Appends are
 * content-addressed and idempotent; the needle is the WHOLE event, so a
 * stranger refused before the house grew and admitted after gets a NEW line:
 * the book is HISTORY, not state.  The door's own event vocabulary is pooled
 * in the universal lexicon -- the door practices the discipline it reports.
 *
 * THE SAME DOOR EMITS (xn_emit_env): the standing scroll leaves as the
 * canonical envelope -- claims split from the canonical bytes themselves,
 * the house's axiom address riding as the offered handshake -- and the arm
 * proves the round trip THROUGH THE REAL JSON PARSER: emit, re-admit, same
 * address, CONFORMING.
 *
 * Truth is a CONDITION OF MOTION: xn_selfprove (arms 110..118) re-derives
 * every law above at every invocation.  NO gate, NO KAT (the kardia pattern).
 * NIH: composes omnia/eidolos (the tongue), verba/json + verba/builder +
 * memoria/arena (the foreign wire, already in the house), verba/lexicon (the
 * vocabulary discipline), numera/idfold (the ONE identity seat).
 * Hexad: kind_passage.  Ring R0. */
module aether_xenos

extern @abi(c-msvc-x64) fn eol_reset() -> i32 from "eidolos.iii"
extern @abi(c-msvc-x64) fn eol_read(addr: u64, len: u64) -> i64 from "eidolos.iii"
